    "description": "Dive into the world of Don’t Drown, an underwater precision platformer. Navigate treacherous landscapes and avoid menacing creatures while balancing your oxygen and health. Line your pockets with treasure at the cost of mobility. Race against time, yourself, and others on the global leaderboards.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Underwater Platforming</h2><br>Traverse through underwater landscapes as a deep sea diver in search of treasure. Being underwater doesn't have to be slow! Use your boost ability to run, swim or sink faster.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/04f41a0e9c48b48de963ab3b83d5015c.poster.avif?t=1736521851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/04f41a0e9c48b48de963ab3b83d5015c.webm?t=1736521851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/04f41a0e9c48b48de963ab3b83d5015c.mp4?t=1736521851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect Treasures</h2><br>Each level contains 1 to 3 treasure chests. Collect at least one to complete the level and enter the leaderboards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/c0f3b610e70a2582ec90554c56282a1e.poster.avif?t=1736521851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/c0f3b610e70a2582ec90554c56282a1e.webm?t=1736521851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/c0f3b610e70a2582ec90554c56282a1e.mp4?t=1736521851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Beware, carrying a treasure increases the effects of gravity. Use your boost to counteract its effects, but be wary of danger.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/48ef3f25df622db2a96df09f19089b12.poster.avif?t=1736521851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/48ef3f25df622db2a96df09f19089b12.webm?t=1736521851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/48ef3f25df622db2a96df09f19089b12.mp4?t=1736521851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dangerous Depths</h2><br>Avoid hazarous obstacles and treacherous wildlife in your pursuit of riches. Be extra careful for it could cost you your life.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/5dadcdcf0ef5a95f05c79f9c05b23431.poster.avif?t=1736521851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/5dadcdcf0ef5a95f05c79f9c05b23431.webm?t=1736521851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398370/extras/5dadcdcf0ef5a95f05c79f9c05b23431.mp4?t=1736521851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Precision Platforming (walk, run, swim, sink)<br></li><li> Difficulty Settings<br></li><li> Constrained movement mechanics<br></li><li> 4 worlds with 6 levels each<br></li><li> Non linear progression (unlock levels in any order)<br></li><li> Controller support and rebindable keybindings<br></li><li> Steam Leaderboards</li></ul>",
